reviewText: It had all of the hits that my grandmother loves, I was very please with it and so was my grandmother!
UN HERMOSO DESPLIEGUE DE UNA DE LAS MEJORES MANIFESTACIONES DE FE Y DEVOCION A NUESTRA MADRE CELESTIAL LA VIRGEN DE GUADALUPE, ARTISTAS COMO LILA DOWS Y MARIA VICTORIA FORMAN PARTE DE ESTE BANQUETE.
